% Example .hgr (hMetis) file
%
% This file format only supports a single weight per hyperedge
% and a single weight per node.
%
%
% #hyperedges #nodes flags
2 3 11
%
%
% 2 hyperedges with weights 15 and 12; each line starts with the weight if second flag is 1
15 1 3
12 1 2 3
%
%
% 3 nodes with weights 100 300 and 140 (only if first flag is 1)
100
300
140
